929
00:38:40,360 --> 00:38:41,960
That's why they're suing Duke An's heir.

930
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:45,080
Was she promised to two families?

931
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,670
- Nonsense!
- Yes, that's right.

932
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,800
That's not true.

933
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:49,570
- Were you sent by the defendant?
- Who's he?

934
00:38:49,920 --> 00:38:50,840
Your Honor,

935
00:38:51,030 --> 00:38:52,150
I have witnesses.

936
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:53,750
Send them in.

937
00:38:53,990 --> 00:38:56,310
- Send them in!
- Send them in!

938
00:39:01,220 --> 00:39:03,060
