941
00:39:05,990 --> 00:39:07,080
Other things aside,

942
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:08,360
should we

943
00:39:08,360 --> 00:39:10,310
try to buy Mr. Zhen over?

944
00:39:11,360 --> 00:39:13,110
What's your decision?

945
00:39:13,240 --> 00:39:15,590
Others can be bought over,

946
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:16,990
(Duke An)

947
00:39:16,990 --> 00:39:18,560
but Zhen Heng of Capital Security

948
00:39:18,960 --> 00:39:20,280
is too rigid and stubborn.

949
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,710
He won't be swayed by anyone.

950
00:39:21,990 --> 00:39:24,000
Sometimes even His Majesty

951
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,880
has to compromise.

952
00:39:26,470 --> 00:39:27,670
That's why

953
00:39:28,510 --> 00:39:30,110
he's got the hardest job

954
00:39:30,110 --> 00:39:31,960
to be the Vice Prefect

955
00:39:32,510 --> 00:39:33,590
of Capital Security.

956
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,110
Your name.

957
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:37,000
Wang Dongsheng, Your Honor.

958
00:39:37,510 --> 00:39:38,790
Occupation.

959
00:39:39,070 --> 00:39:41,880
I'm a waiter at a wonton shop.

960
00:39:42,530 --> 00:39:43,800
Answer my question.

961
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:45,400
What

962
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:46,590
