963
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:54,520
I was by the river,

964
00:39:55,070 --> 00:39:56,110
but it was too dark.

965
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:57,440
I barely saw anything.

966
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:59,150
You're in court.

967
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,400
Do not lie.

968
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:02,880
What exactly did you see?

969
00:40:05,240 --> 00:40:06,210
I didn't get a good look.

970
00:40:09,420 --> 00:40:10,820
(Ji Chongli, Ji Chongyi's Brother)

971
00:40:13,240 --> 00:40:14,110
But I've

972
00:40:14,110 --> 00:40:15,560
said in public

973
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:17,750
Young Master Ji pushed Miss Si.

974
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:19,840
I heard

975
00:40:20,150 --> 00:40:21,150
your mother is

976
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:22,630
old and lame.

977
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,080
What do you want?

978
00:40:28,920 --> 00:40:30,960
It was too dark that night.

979
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,790
You barely saw anything.

980
00:40:40,440 --> 00:40:41,280
Jiang Si,

981
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:43,110
