985
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:54,230
Greetings, Your Honor.

986
00:40:55,630 --> 00:40:57,150
I did see Miss Si

987
00:40:57,150 --> 00:40:58,270
fall into the river,

988
00:40:58,990 --> 00:41:00,110
but

989
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,750
she slipped and fell.

990
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,160
Song Lin,

991
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,360
did you see it clearly?

992
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:08,110
Yes, Your Honor.

993
00:41:08,510 --> 00:41:10,270
I got a good look at what happened.

994
00:41:11,360 --> 00:41:12,710
You two may leave.

995
00:41:12,960 --> 00:41:14,520
Yes, Your Honor.

996
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,110
Looks like someone

997
00:41:31,280 --> 00:41:32,880
pushed me into the water

998
00:41:33,070 --> 00:41:34,590
and suborned the witnesses.

999
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:36,040
It was dark and slippery.

1000
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,630
Their view might've been affected.

1001
00:41:38,880 --> 00:41:40,710
Great wits have short memories, huh?

1002
00:41:41,190 --> 00:41:42,440
I held a lantern that night.

1003
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,150
If it could shine a light

1004
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,400
on your dirty business,

1005
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:47,110
