1006
00:41:47,110 --> 00:41:48,520
You're lying!

1007
00:41:51,470 --> 00:41:53,920
Your Honor, we did bicker.

1008
00:41:54,070 --> 00:41:54,920
Miss Si

1009
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,270
lost her temper,

1010
00:41:56,440 --> 00:41:57,400
and she somehow

1011
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,840
fell into the river.

1012
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:00,150
Miss Si,

1013
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,710
I know you're mad at me,

1014
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,720
