1018
00:42:11,030 --> 00:42:13,440
Your Honor, I have one more witness.

1019
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,480
Who else?

1020
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,750
The girl Ji Chongyi dated that night,

1021
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:22,230
Qiaoniang.

1022
00:42:22,670 --> 00:42:23,510
Right.

1023
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:25,110
She was the closest person

1024
00:42:25,110 --> 00:42:26,040
