1025
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:27,680
Guards.

1026
00:42:28,470 --> 00:42:29,590
Send Sun Qiaoniang in.

1027
00:42:30,630 --> 00:42:32,150
Send Qiaoniang in!

1028
00:42:41,760 --> 00:42:43,150
I, Sun Qiaoniang, greet you,

1029
00:42:43,840 --> 00:42:44,920
Your Honor.

1030
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:46,750
Sun Qiaoniang,

1031
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:48,150
answer my question.

1032
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:51,320
Did Ji Chongyi push Jiang Si

1033
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,310
into the river?

1034
00:42:52,510 --> 00:42:55,110
Qiaoniang, tell the truth.

1035
00:42:55,360 --> 00:42:56,880
I'm here. Don't be afraid.

1036
00:43:01,220 --> 00:43:05,100
(The End)

